To move a Microsoft.Insights/workbook (Azure Monitor workbook) to a new subscription - open the workbook in the Azure portal - enter edit mode - use the Save As option - and then select the desired new subscription in the save form - essentially you are creating a new copy of the workbook in the new subscription with the same data and configuration.
